title: DDFP 120: Hurting RG3 & dancing Ray Lewis
itunes:title: DDFP 120: Hurting RG3 & dancing Ray Lewis
description:
Shek & Rank jump in Studio 66 with pals Handsome Hank and 'Around The Leaguers' Dan Hanzus & Marc Sessler for some quick reaction to the wild-card round playoff games.  Subjects include: RG3's knee; Ray Lewis' dancing; and the short-term prospects of the Seahawks.  Plus, some further discussion about the Best Appetizer of 2012 from last week's Sheky Awards - and the return of Black Tie's shoutout.
